item.description:
Description An attacker can make a private memo into a public memo in order to view it. All the attacker needs to know is the memo ID and they can make a PATCH request to /api/memo/&lt;memo ID&gt; with the following request data:
{&quot;id&quot;:&lt;MEMO ID&gt;,&quot;visibility&quot;:&quot;PUBLIC&quot;,&quot;resourceIdList&quot;:[]}
Then the attacker can visit the memo URL &amp; view the memo data of the victim. The memo URL format is similar to this: https://demo.usememos.com/m/&lt;MEMO ID&gt;.
